{"tid":1810546,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"還柙抗爭者寫信 謝手足聲援","createTime":"2020-01-04T03:36:17.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-04T03:56:20.000Z","uid":25558,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"a232121a4f5f56ec678eb9f7f1f962feb35c7cfb","tid":1810546,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-04T03:36:17.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200104/NLGPB4GDAE22HW5HFE2K452PXA/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200104%2FNLGPB4GDAE22HW5HFE2K452PXA%2F&d=GO0vWKcqTLT5bpzdAOrPDllQFaTeS91CmK6iy9gpT9M%3D&h=2bc3e208\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200104%2FNLGPB4GDAE22HW5HFE2K452PXA%2F&h=b5620a63\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200104/NLGPB4GDAE22HW5HFE2K452PXA/</a><br />\n<br />\n還柙抗爭者寫信 謝手足聲援<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20200104/large/1578080608_4af4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20200104%2Flarge%2F1578080608_4af4.jpg&h=20f6f6f8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n大批市民平安夜到荔枝角收押所報佳音，向被扣押的手足表達「齊上齊落，不離不棄」的訊息。<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】反送中運動至今近七個月，警方濫捕成癮，逾6,000人被捕。大批市民上月趁聖誕節前夕，到荔枝角收押所外集會，數千人隔着鐵絲網，以《願榮光歸香港》的歌聲聲援還柙人士，也有不少市民寫聖誕卡。一名現於荔枝角還柙的前線抗爭者，親筆寫信予工黨立法會議員張超雄，感謝港人，「我係喺荔枝角還柙嘅一位前線抗爭者，其實都唔係第一次寫畀你哋，但其實要對你哋嘅感激，點都講唔完！」<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：爆眼教師：黑警係教育失敗產物<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n向監房朋友解答抗爭問題<br />\n<br />\n該名抗爭者在信中稱，<span style=\"color: orange;\">「12月20號嘅晚上，由10點鐘開始聽到你哋嘅聲援」，「以前佢（羈押人士）會覺得好嘈、好煩，至少今次（20號）佢聽到『手足，我撐你』、『煲底見』、『釋放義士，還我公義』，從窗邊望出去可以見到一盞盞由手機燈形成嘅星海，你哋喺出面『和你寫』嘅聖誕卡，好多朋友見到都好驚訝</span>&hellip;&hellip;有朋友問我「榮光」點唱，但本人比較怕醜，冇去唱畀佢哋聽。」<br />\n<br />\n他又表示「好多喺監房嘅朋友仔去問我，我哋爭取啲咩，而最多嘅問題係問有冇錢收&hellip;&hellip;每一個早上我都會打開電視睇now新聞&hellip;&hellip;睇鏗鏘集、頭條新聞，啲朋友一路睇，一路問煲底、Be Water、TG、連登、PePe嘅詞語代表嘅嘢，有人喺電視上睇到警方亂棍打市民，之後講咗句『乜警察可以咁打人嘅咩？』而我只答咗佢一句『𠵱度影到嘅只係你睇到嘅小部份，仲有好多好多你係睇唔到。』最後，他寄語港人團結，「我喺監獄都唔放棄，香港人，因為團結，我哋先有今日，所以革命未完，你哋點可以放棄呢？」<br />\n<br />\n■記者譚靜雯<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail_r.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail_r.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3ae1ca33ce7d8f52ae9a9086a61432ab2b9aa648","tid":1810546,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-04T03:42:43.000Z","msg":"日期：2020年1月5日 星期日<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">新春上水和你行</span><br />\n時間 ： 1500<br />\n地點:上水一號花園(龍豐對面)-&gt;上水黨鐵站C出口<br />\n活動TG頻道：<a href=\"https://t.me/wedontlikegreygoodstrader\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fwedontlikegreygoodstrader&d=GO0vWKcqTLT5bpzdAOrPDllQFaTeS91CmK6iy9gpT9M%3D&h=924f3e9d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/wedontlikegreygoodstrader</a><br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">（已獲不反對通知書）</span><br />\n<br />\n==============<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">銅鑼灣 x 灣仔稅局 和你Lunch</span><br />\n日期：2020年1月6日 星期一<br />\n時間 ： 1245 <br />\n地點 ：時代廣場集合/灣仔稅務局"},{"pid":"49eba1b3b4c3c22ee2ee31a4b27f4864500770fb","tid":1810546,"uid":83910,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-04T03:43:40.000Z","msg":"其實去收押所活動可以定期攪"},{"pid":"350d74361092ae87cacc758d13287159756b1a71","tid":1810546,"uid":230663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-04T03:51:26.000Z","msg":"手足<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" clas